---
// src/components/Services.astro
---

<section id="servicios" class="w-full bg-[#f8f9fa] py-24 px-8 md:px-16 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-10 mb-16">
      
      <div class="md:w-3/5 reveal-text">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-[2px] bg-slate-800"></span>
          <span class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-slate-500 uppercase">Nuestros Servicios</span>
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="font-karma text-5xl md:text-6xl text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="font-weight: 600;">
          Soluciones metálicas <br /> para cada necesidad
        </h2>
        
        <p class="font-inter text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Trabajamos con particulares, empresas y naves industriales en toda Andalucía que necesitan estructuras duraderas, seguras y con un acabado impecable.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-2/5 flex md:justify-end reveal-card delay-100">
        <a 
          href="#proyectos" 
          class="font-sans group inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-900 text-white text-base font-medium rounded-full px-8 py-4 hover:bg-slate-800 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span class="transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:-translate-x-1.5">
            Conocer más sobre nosotros
          </span>
          
          <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-white/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:rotate-45">
            
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-6 group-hover:-translate-y-6">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 19.5 15-15m0 0H8.25m11.25 0v11.25" />
            </svg>

            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="absolute w-4 h-4 -translate-x-6 translate-y-6 transition-transform duration-300 ease-out group-hover:translate-x-0 group-hover:translate-y-0">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 19.5 15-15m0 0H8.25m11.25 0v11.25" />
            </svg>
            
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] reveal-card delay-100">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-800 mb-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Industrial</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Diseño, fabricación y montaje de naves, cubiertas y entreplantas metálicas para optimizar tu espacio de trabajo y soportar grandes cargas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] reveal-card delay-200">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-800 mb-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 6h16M4 10h16M4 14h16M4 18h16M8 6v12M16 6v12"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Residencial</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Puertas, cancelas, vallados perimetrales y barandillas a medida. Combinamos máxima seguridad con un diseño estético para tu hogar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.06)] reveal-card delay-300">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-800 mb-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M14.121 14.121L19 19m-7-7l7-7m-7 7l-2.879 2.879M12 12L9.121 9.121m0 5.758a3 3 0 10-4.243-4.243 3 3 0 004.243 4.243z"></path>
        </svg>
        <h3 class="font-sans text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">A Medida</h3>
        <p class="font-sans text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
          Escaleras interiores y exteriores, mobiliario industrial y piezas decorativas exclusivas en acero, hierro y forja adaptadas a tu visión.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>